<h2 id="overview-of-the-project">Overview of the project</h2>

<p>Flutter client for eletronic school register (Classeviva) management using clean architecture.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Simple and beautiful</li>
  <li>Useful charts and stats about grades, absences, etcâ€¦</li>
  <li>Dark &amp; Light theme</li>
  <li>Notifications when there is a new event (new grade, new event, etc..)</li>
  <li>Data persistency</li>
  <li>Final grades</li>
  <li>Multi language support (Italian &amp; English) and localizaiton</li>
</ul>

<p><br /></p>

